data.description: Classic rancher with land!!!  This brick rancher is a country charmer on over 4 acres.  The front yard is delightfully landscaped with a large horseshoe driveway around the home.  The acreage is great for the family, hunting, pets, or even farm life.   The family room has been converted into a spacious bedroom but can be converted back easily to suit your lifestyle.  Head downstairs to more finished square footage, a bedroom, tons of storage and workshop/laundry space.  Did I mention a new metal roof???!!!!!
